    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1939-09-21T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1939-09-21T10:00:00-05:00" n="478"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d478">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.51/1148: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-09-21T11:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 21, 1939—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received September 21—11 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>156. Notified Wachholtz last night of allocation of 5 million credit by
                    Export-Import Bank. He accepted with appreciation and will make public
                    announcement here today. He plans to send purchasing agent to the United States
                    in the immediate future.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bowers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
